description:
The Modulxo common library to be used in all the Modulxo parts.
(containing model definition, custom exception types und much more)
----------------------------------------------------------
This project is intended for personal usage only - therefore the documentation is not necessarily complete.
Any programer is free to use this library anyway - but there is no support, update plans or similar.
----------------------------------------------------------
